    <Title><![CDATA[Easy to use Workplace]]></Title>
    <Text name="Text0">
      <links>
        <link name="link0" internal="true" type="A">
          <target><![CDATA[/sites/default/tutorial/]]></target>
          <uuid>f51baae8-3a95-11e9-bd84-0242ac11002b</uuid>
        </link>
      </links>
      <content><![CDATA[<p>OpenCms 11 comes with a rewritten power-user backoffice called the Workplace.</p>
<p>With improved inline editing options such as <strong>drag &amp; drop for images</strong> it's easier than ever for content managers to create great looking websites with OpenCms.</p>
<p>Check out the <a href="%(link0)">tutorial</a> for a quick intro about the use of the editing features.</p>]]></content>
